verbose_text: The ATRX and CHIC1 expression levels in the hPES-2 ' cells at P60 were higher than those in the hPES-2 cells at P60, but were decreased in the hPES-2 ' cells at P70 and were as low as in those in the hPES-2 cells at P60, suggesting that a low XIST RNA expression in the hPES-2 ' cells at P70 had occurred (XREF_FIG).
